# Coyote Linux 4 System Configuration
#
# This file documents the configuration partition layout.
# The actual configuration is stored in JSON format.
#
# Configuration Partition Structure:
# ----------------------------------
# /mnt/config/
# ├── system.json           # Main system configuration
# ├── webadmin-users.json   # Web admin user credentials
# └── backups/              # Configuration backups
#     └── *.json
#
# The configuration partition is mounted read-only during normal
# operation and only briefly mounted read-write when saving changes.
